GAIN Fitness tailors programs & guides you to your goals by turning your smartphone into a personal trainer. Over 1M people have used our  apps, en route to disrupting a $20B+ global growth industry. 

We're the first scalable platform to crossover fitness styles—bodybuilding, bootcamps, yoga, sport-specific & rehab. We target & sell these via In-App Purchase.

Our team of ex-Googlers and serial entrepreneurs is supported by investor/advisors from Google, YouTube, Paypal, Crunch Fitness & TRX.
startup.high_concept: Digital Personal Training Platform

CapLinked gives companies secure cloud-based tools to manage business transactions (such as a capital raise, asset sale, or M&A deal), conduct investor reporting, and network with finance professionals.

startup.name: Wedding Album+
startup.product_desc:
The easiest and most fun way to collect wedding photos from your guests. No login required, we use geolocation and time of day to collect photos and stream the live and to an online gallery. 

To demo, download the app http://alpha.albumpl.us/we-want-your-candids/ enter code "ANGEL" when prompted. Code is only necessary for distributed test galleries. Otherwise the app opens directly to the event you are attending, based on location and time of day (not proximity to other users).
startup.high_concept: The easiest way to collect photos from your guests.

startup.name: Genomera
startup.product_desc:
Clinical trials & health science studies at Internet scale.

The bottleneck restricting health science discovery frustrates two sides of the market:
   - Consumers want evidence-based answers, speed, and engagement.
   - Researchers need efficiency and scale, as well as cohorts and data.

Genomera provides online study operations and a social-powered marketplace, connecting participants with researchers.

Helping consumers, academics, & commercial orgs grow evidence to answer health questions.
startup.high_concept: Clinical Trials at Internet Scale

startup.name: GPX Software
startup.product_desc:
Financial planning spreadsheets are a primary reason why 5 out 6 small business fail.
"Xambrosius BI Tools" by GPX Software brings enterprise featured BI to small businesses at a small business price by providing multiple pre-programmed fiscal planning templates, dashboards, analytics, step-by-step wizards, and web services to data-mine comparable company and personnel facts. Xambrosius cuts GIGO while reducing data entry and analysis time from over forty to less than four hours.
startup.high_concept: Xambrosius-The financial planning & analysis tool for small business-BI for the Little Guy

Our self-serve website enables developers to plan, control, and optimize their user acquisition campaigns.

startup.name: Cambridge Temperature Concepts
startup.product_desc:
DuoFertility is a home fertility monitoring service, proven equally effective as IVF for half of all IVF patients (with peer reviewed publications).  DuoFertility costs 1/10th what IVF does, and is suitable for 80% of all infertile couples (of which there are about 1.5M couples/year EU+US). CE and FDA cleared.

DuoFertility retails online at www.DuoFertility.com and in the UK through Boots Pharmacy.  The price is £495 (~$800), and if you're not pregnant in 12 months we give your money back.
startup.high_concept: Home fertility service proven as effective as IVF

startup.name: WP Engine
startup.product_desc:
WPEngine is a WordPress-only hosting company focussed on speed, scalability, security, and service. We address the gap between low-cost, low-end hosting and expensive, custom hosting.

Went cash-flow positive in 7 months, then made hires and went positive again in 6 months. Now that we've shown the model is profitable, it's time to switch to growth-mode.
startup.high_concept: Heroku for WordPress

startup.name: CareSpeak Communications
startup.product_desc:
CareSpeak's disease management platform uses 2-way sms-to-web to facilitate real time communication/data exchange between patient & circle-of-care team, leading to improved patient outcomes. 

Patients notified via 2way SMS to take medication or measure/report biometrics. If not reported within specified time, escalation alerts sent to caregivers or monitoring service. Patients further engaged via educational and motivational messages. Incentives incorporated via phone allowances & co-pay cards.
startup.high_concept: Improving patient outcomes via 2way text-to-web mHealth platform
